parameters.name: startedTimeFilter
parameters.description: List all command executions that started any time before or after the date and time that you specify. The date and time uses the format yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm. after (string) --- Filter to display command executions that started or completed only after a particular date and time. before (string) --- Filter to display command executions that started or completed only before a particular date and time.
